title: 327 - Remembering "Grandma Gwen"
description:
In this episode, the guys alongside Jemal “The 9 To 5 King Millionaire” discuss the lessons learned from Grandma Gwen. 

17:30 - “You can’t guarantee anything, but be sure to try your hardest.”

22:36 - With the days you have being numbered by God, be sure to execute the highest level possible on all opportunities you have.

28:30 - “Every issue isn’t your issue. You don’t have energy to use on things that don’t involve or concern you.”
